data.description:
Discover the epitome of luxury living in the highly sought-after Bella Charca subdivision at 3009 Fieldwood Dr. A true masterpiece by Vale-Irvin, this custom-built residence redefines elegance and comfort.

Step into the grandeur of the living room with its impressive 22ft ceiling and a captivating floor-to-ceiling stone fireplace that radiates warmth throughout. The chef's kitchen is a culinary masterpiece, featuring top-of-the-line appliances and expansive countertops. Stained concrete floors add a touch of sophistication while ensuring practicality. The bathrooms boast custom cabinetry, adding an elegant flair.

Unwind in the primary suite, complete with a large garden tub and a custom walk-in shower. Situated on a sprawling 1/3 acre lot, the possibilities for outdoor enjoyment are endless. The convenient 3-car garage provides ample space for vehicles and projects. Embrace the luxurious lifestyle offered by this exceptional property.
